\strong{Mode anchor, not mean.} As with \code{\link{ssjplss}} and
\code{\link{ibslss}}, once \eqn{\nu \ne 0} the location \eqn{\xi} is the
\emph{mode anchor} of the asymmetric density, not its mean direction;
